    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In churches, cloths and coverings used to conceal paintings, sculptures, and other items of luxury and beauty during the solemn Lenten season. For the curtains used to conceal the altar during Lent, use "Lenten veils."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
